data.description: Here is an opportunity to live close to all that downtown Fishers has to offer. This 3 bedroom/2 full bath home has the space you need. You will love the feel of the light and airy remodeled main floor that has luxury vinyl plank and neutral paint. Extra large living room. Remodeled kitchen with new cabinets, countertops, appliances, and sink. Breakfast room overlooks backyard. Overhang on kitchen counters perfect for bar stools. New carpet on stairs and upstairs hallway. All bedrooms are upstairs along with laundry room. New A/C installed July 2023. Community pool is steps away from the front door. Convenient to all downtown attractions, Nickel Plate Trail and  major roads. HSE Schools.
